'''Tolkien Calendar 1996''' was published by Slaski Klub Fantasyki, Poland ([[Polish Tolkien Society]]). The calendar features illustrations by [[Ryszard Derdziński]], [[Arkadiusz Jubala]], [[Helena Strolkowska]], [[Małgorzata Pudlik]], [[Maciej Wygnanski]], and [[Aleksandra Jagielowica]]. Reckonings in standard dates, the [[Buckland]] calendar, new reckoning of [[Aragorn|King Elessar]], and the [[Calendar of Imladris]]. 

* Dimensions: 11 3/4 x 16 1/2 inches
* White comb-bound at top
